---
title: Spinner
---

p.-text Spinners are animated circles that let users know when information is saving or loading.

h3 Examples
p.-text To render a spinner, use the class <code>a-spinner</code>.

h3 Backdrop
p.-text Wrap spinners in <code>a-backdrop</code> to overlay content similar to a modal.
h4 Base
.example.-mb--3
  .a-backdrop.-p--6(style="position:relative;height:25rem;")
    svg(class=`a-spinner -text--inverse`,viewBox=`0 0 66 66`)
      title Loading
      circle(class=`path`,cx=`33`,cy=`33`,r=`30`,fill=`none`,stroke-width=`6`)
  :code(lang="html")
    <div class="a-backdrop">
      <svg class="a-spinner -text--inverse" viewBox="0 0 66 66">
        <title>Loading</title>
        <circle class="path" cx="33" cy="33" r="30" fill="none" stroke-width="6"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>

h4 Inverse
p.-text Apply the class <code>-inverse</code> to render spinners on light backgrounds.
.example.-mb--3
  .a-backdrop.-inverse.-p--6(style="position:relative;height:25rem;")
    svg(class=`a-spinner -text--primary`,viewBox=`0 0 66 66`)
      title Loading
      circle(class=`path`,cx=`33`,cy=`33`,r=`30`,fill=`none`,stroke-width=`6`)
  :code(lang="html")
    <div class="a-backdrop -inverse">
      <svg class="a-spinner -text--primary" viewBox="0 0 66 66">
        <title>Loading</title>
        <circle class="path" cx="33" cy="33" r="30" fill="none" stroke-width="6"></circle>
      </svg>
    </div>

h3 Contextual

h4 Spinners in Buttons
.example.-mb--3
  .-p--3
    button(class=`a-btn -mr--3`)
      .a-btn__content
        span Button
        svg(class=`a-spinner -text--muted`,viewBox=`0 0 66 66`)
          title Loading
          circle(class=`path`,cx=`33`,cy=`33`,r=`30`,fill=`none`,stroke-width=`6`)
    button(class='a-btn -small -mr--3')
      .a-btn__content
        span Small
        svg(class=`a-spinner -text--muted -xs`,viewBox=`0 0 66 66`)
          title Loading
          circle(class=`path`,cx=`33`,cy=`33`,r=`30`,fill=`none`,stroke-width=`6`)
    button(class='a-btn -large -mr--3')
      .a-btn__content
        span Large
        svg(class=`a-spinner -text--muted -sm--2`,viewBox=`0 0 66 66`)
          title Loading
          circle(class=`path`,cx=`33`,cy=`33`,r=`30`,fill=`none`,stroke-width=`6`)
  :code(lang='html')
    <button class="a-btn">
      <div class="a-btn__content">
        <span>Button</span>
